This downloader provides custom additional content to the Battlefield 2 modification "Forgotten Hope 2".
The content, i.e. the additional maps and minimods are provided by their respective creators. They are not provided by and in no way associated with the official Forgotten Hope 2 modding team.
For help and support for an addon, please contact the creators at the link given in that addon's tab.
